# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
We want a keys[i] -> values[i] dictionary to easily encrypt a character in O(1) and a word in O(n) where n is the length of the word.

Similarly, for an O(1) decryption we want to pre-process all of the strings in the given dictionary upon Encrypter construction.

The Encrytper would run in O(n) where n is the number of strings in the dictionary. 
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
