* We can solve this problem with Dijktra's algo thats quite obvious but when the weights of the graph is not large or it limited to small number lets say k i.e. weight ranges from 1 to k we can use BFS. 
* Here in this question its given that weight is either 0 or 1 so instead of using Dijktra we can go for 01 BFS. 
* Attaching some video links and tutorial links which you can refer to understand this concept.
