# Intuition
basically i saw the hint in te box ..

# Approach
making a graph with nodes as matrix points and edges cost is the matrix value and now using dijkastra algortihm like approach. Here the only different thing i did was to use a single dimensional array instead of a multidimensional array.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
nlogn

- Space complexity:
