# Intuition
Get minumum distance bewteen node like 0 and 1 BFS travesal in tree to get level.

# Approach
Push node which is 0 at front of queue and 1 at end of queue becuase all node with 0 have same distance or level so they can processed simulatniously in BFS traversal.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
o m*n

- Space complexity:
o m*n

