# Intitution
Element with same first letter cannot form valid combination as replecing them create the same name again.
Therefore, there is no relation between element with same first letter. So, we will divide them into different set with same first letter.
Then we will compare every set and and check the common element because common element also leads to same invalid sequence **if we have "cat","car" and "rat" so replacing c with r in "cat" and "rat"will make the same letters again and even if we replace "car" and "rat" thet will also creat "cat" that is invalid**. So we will simply dont count them in result .
take intersection and dont count them while calculating the combination.
