# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Our aim is to maximize the xor of all the elements present in the array. One approach is to step by step try to increase the maximum xor output possible. By maximizing the output we mean to increase the number of 1 in as many bits as we can, prioritizing the higher significant bits. 

However, we can try another approach in which instead of really going deep in our computational search, we just predict what the maximum output value can possible be by simply noticing the number of 1 bits for every bit position. 
You will realize that all you need to do is get the bitwise 'OR' of all the elements present in the array 
